 anied by deep breathing.\n\nTai chi\, also called tai chi chuan\, is 
 a non-competitive\, self-paced system of gentle physical exercise and
  stretching. Each posture flows into the next without pause\, ensurin
 g that your body is in constant motion.         \n\nPlease sign up on
  the Village App.
