SUMMARY:Tai Chi (45m) - Michael
DESCRIPTION:Instructor: Michael Breivold\nRoom: OV Group Fitness 2\nLo
 cation: Ocotillo Village\nTai chi is an ancient Chinese tradition tha
 t\, today\, is practiced as a graceful form of exercise. It involves 
 a series of movements performed in a slow\, focused manner and accomp
 anied by deep breathing. \n\nTai chi\, also called tai chi chuan\, is
  a non-competitive\, self-paced system of gentle physical exercise an
 d stretching. Each posture flows into the next without pause\, ensuri
 ng that your body is in constant motion.     \n\nPlease sign up on th
 e Village App.
END:VEVENT
